c: 2
v: 185
t: "Aggur n ﾃ氾貌mvan, ideg d irs Leqwﾃｴan, d nnhaya i medden, d abeggen n nnhaya akked ufraz. Win segwen iwalan illul ed waggur, a t iuzum. Win iuvnen ne$ illan ippinig, annect n wussan nniven. ﾃ貌bbi Ib$a yawen sshala, ur awen Ib$a ara cedda. A pfukem tallit, a pkabrem ﾃ貌bbi imi kwen Inha, amar a ppesnemmrem"